Class Summary
NodeBase This class handle the list of tap nodes TapNode.
NodeMap This class wraps a LinkedHashMap of TAP nodes.
TapNode Manage a TAP node: - get the node description (capabilities, tables) - check the availability - convert node responses in JSON All data related to that node are stored in baseDirectory.
